Package cz.ive.gui

Classes providing main part of the GUI and painting of application events.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
GraphicInfo Iface representing object specific informations for proper visualisation.
GraphicTemplate This iface represents graphical template common to all equaly visualised objects.
Gui GUI interface
Viewpoint Iface for definition of the graphical viewpoint.
 

Class Summary
AbstractGraphicInfo Abstract implementation of the graphic info iface.
ActorGraphicInfo GraphicInfo specialized for drawing the actors.
AnimatedGraphicInfo Implementation of the GraphicInfo specialized for viewing objects depending on the value of a particular attribute.
AnimatedPanel Abstract implementation of GUI panel, that supports backbuffer and its filling from another thread
AnimatedTemplate GraphicTemplate implementation for multistate images.
DelegatedGraphicInfo Implementation of GraphicInfo used only for templates IveObjects.
GeniusTree Subwindow for tree of geniuses and their goal trees
GraphAreaPanel Implementation of GUI panel, that can show Graph locations.
GuiCalendar Subwinodw with a gui representation of the calendar.
GuiCalendar.EventInfo Helper storage class holding the Calendar event Info.
GuiLog Extension of JPanel which displays graphic representation of hierarchical log
HiLODPanel Implementation of GUI panel, that can show hi-LOD locations.
LocationTree Tree view for Loaction hierarchy visualisation.
LogFilter Panel with group of checkboxes.
MainFrame MainFrame of the application
ProcessorLoadPanel Simple processor load JPanel
StaticTemplate GraphicsTemplate implementation for still images
WayPointGraphicInfo GraphicInfo specialized for WayPoint drawing.
ZoomScrollPanel Skeleton implementation of GUI panel that can be zoomed and scrolled.
 

Package cz.ive.gui Description

Classes providing main part of the GUI and painting of application events. Paints all graphics components on application startup and mannage user operations.
